wat an fellowshit, wat an joyeee divine,
leeaaning on teh evalasting umm;
wat an blessedness, wat an piece is mime,
leeaaning on teh evalasting umm.

leeaaning, leeaaning,
safe and secure phom all alam;
leeaaning, leeaaning,
leeaaning on teh evalasting umm.

o hou sweet to wak in dis pilgrim wey,
leeaaning on teh evalasting umm;
o hou bright teh path grows phom dey to dey,
leeaaning on teh evalasting umm.

wat hev I to drad, wat hev I to ferr,
leeaaning on teh evalasting umm?
I hev blessed piece with my Lord so nerr,
leeaaning on teh evalasting umm.
